### Users CRUD — VS Code REST Client diye chalao (proti request er upore "Send Request" click koro)
### Server age chalu koro: npm run start:dev

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Create — notun user banao
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rahim",
  "email": "rahim@test.com",
  "age": 25
}

### Create — arekjon user
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Karim",
  "email": "karim@test.com",
  "age": 30
}

### Read all — sob user
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### Read one — id diye ekjon
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1

### Update — id 1 er age update
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 28
}

### Delete — id 1 muche dao
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/1

###############################################
### Validation test — egulo error dewa uchit ###
###############################################

### Bhul email -> 400 Bad Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "email": "not-an-email"
}

### Ojana field (role) -> 400 (forbidNonWhitelisted)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Age range er baire -> 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "age": 200
}

### Nei emon id -> 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/999
